    <h1>Help Us Spread the Word</h1>
    <a id="twitter" href="https://twitter.com/Kubmo" target="_blank"><%= image_tag 'twitter.png',:title => 'Twitter'  %></a>
    <a id="facebook" href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Kubmo/502648673114461" target= "_blank"><%= image_tag 'facebook.png',:title => 'Facebook'  %></a>
    <a id="pinterest" href="https://pinterest.com/kubmo/" target="_blank"><%= image_tag 'pinterest.png',:title => 'Pinterest'  %></a>
    <div id="spread_examples">
      <h2>Send a tweet</h2>
      <p>"Help 10 women in Kenya get their ventures off the ground through mentorship and technology! http://www.kubmo.org/ @kubmo"</p>
      <h2>Post on Facebook</h2>
      <p>"Kubmo is a company empowering young women in Kenya to become independent by getting their own company off the ground. Starting August 27th, they will be going through a three day workshop, followed by a year long program of mentorship and smart phone access. See the website for more details on how you can get involved! http://www.kubmo.org/"</p>
      <h2>Send an email</h2>
      <p>"Kubmo was a company started to help young women in Kenya become financially independent. The two co-founders found out that many women in Kenya have the will power and desire to start their own companies, but cannot do so without access to smartphones and advice from other women who have done the same. </p>
      <p>So they created a program, along with a non-profit in Kenya, where 10 women in Nairobi will go through an intensive workshop, receive a smartphone with data, and have access to a network of mentors. The first workshop is happening on August 27th. You can see a profile for each young woman at Kubmo.org. </p>
      <p>In order to make this happen, and allow these 10 young women to be successful, Kubmo needs to raise $2,500.  Here is a breakdown of what you could sponsor for one of the Kubmo entrepreneurs:</p>
      <h3>Phone package: $114</h3>
      <h3>Room and board for the workshop: $109</h3>
      <h3>Workshop materials: $35</h3>
      <h3>The entire experience for one young woman: $258</h3>
      <p>Please help make this workshop a reality by sponsoring a part of the Kubmo experience for one of the entrepreneurs. You can make your donation at Kubmo.org, and change the lives of one of these ten Kenyan women. </p>
      <p>Thanks for your support!"</p>
    </div>
  </div>
